Conclusion
You've successfully built an AI-powered test suggestion pipeline that:

Analyzes code changes using Git and AST parsing
Extracts function complexity metrics
Generates intelligent test suggestions using local AI models
Produces actionable reports for improving test coverage
This pipeline can be integrated into CI/CD workflows to automatically suggest tests for every pull request, helping DevOps teams maintain high code quality and catch potential issues before deployment. The use of local AI models (Ollama) ensures data privacy and eliminates external API dependencies.

Key Takeaways:

Code analysis can be automated using Python's AST module
Local AI models provide powerful code understanding capabilities
